msgstr "经过12个阶段后，你将开始受到伤害。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Every 5 minutes, warp sickness advances. "
msgstr "每5分钟，跃迁病会加剧。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"You'll teleport to a random location with three missions: find the exit, "
"kill enemies, and find warp shards. "
msgstr "你将传送至随机位置，并有三项任务：找到出口、击杀敌人、寻找跃迁碎片。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Use the Warp Obelisk to begin an expedition. "
msgstr "使用跃迁方尖碑开始远征。"

#: .\heart.lua
