#: .\items.json
msgid "Labs Catalyst"
msgid_plural "Labs Catalysts"
msgstr[0] "实验室催化剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Labs Catalyst'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A bit of warp power, a magnetic stripe keycard from a dangerous place, and a"
" little hope, blended well. This item is required to begin a Labs "
"expedition, and is consumed when leaving."
msgstr "一点扭曲能量、一张来自危险地带的磁条钥匙卡，再加上少许希望，充分混合。此物品是开启实验室远征所必需的，并在离开时消耗。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Heartseed"
msgid_plural "Heartseeds"
msgstr[0] "核心种子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heartseed'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A whorl of black stone that feels impossibly heavy for its size. Activate "
"this on your island to place the Heart of the Island, the catalyst of future"
" upgrades."
msgstr "一团黑色石头的漩涡，其重量相对于体积来说重得不可思议。在你的岛屿上激活此物以放置岛屿之心，这是未来升级的催化剂。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "infinity tree sapling"
msgid_plural "infinity tree saplings"
msgstr[0] "无限树苗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infinity tree sapling'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A fragile little wisp of a sapling. Its leaves shake and quiver, shimmering "
"with strange energies. Activate this on your island to place an infinity "
"tree, which can be used as a catalyst to turn material tokens into wooden "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"一株脆弱的小树苗，如微光般摇曳。它的叶子颤抖摆动，闪烁着奇异能量。在你的岛屿上激活此物以放置一棵无限树，可用作催化剂将物质代币转化为木质资源。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "infinity stone source"
msgid_plural "infinity stone sources"
msgstr[0] "无限石源"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infinity stone source'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A crackling little cluster of pebbles that spark as they knock together, "
"tumbling about from forces unseen. Activate this on your island to place an "
"infinity stone, which can be used as a catalyst to turn material tokens into"
" stony and earthen resources."
msgstr ""
"一小簇噼啪作响的卵石，相互碰撞时迸发火花，在无形力量作用下翻滚不停。在你的岛屿上激活此物以放置一块无限石，可用作催化剂将物质代币转化为石质与土质资源。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "infinity ore crucible"
msgid_plural "infinity ore crucibles"
msgstr[0] "无限矿石坩埚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infinity ore crucible'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A miniature tangle of metal that resembles a dust bunny made of barbed wire."
" It twists in upon itself endlessly, folding and unfolding in ways that "
"don't seem possible. Activate this on your island to place an infinity ore, "
"which can be used as a catalyst to turn material tokens into metal "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"一团微型金属缠结物，形似由带刺铁丝构成的尘团。它无尽地自我扭曲，以看似不可能的方式折叠与展开。在你的岛屿上激活此物以放置一块无限矿石，可用作催化剂将物质代币转化为金属资源。"

#: .\items.json
