msgid_plural "Survivor's Contracts"
msgstr[0] "幸存者契约"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Survivor's Contract"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A contract signed in zombie blood, proving the holder to be a true survivor."
" Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Two Missions: Every "
"expedition now offers 2 randomly assigned bonus missions."
msgstr "一份用僵尸血签署的契约，证明持有者是真正的幸存者。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁双重任务：每次远征现在提供2个随机分配的额外任务。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Mercenary's Contract"
msgid_plural "Mercenary's Contracts"
msgstr[0] "佣兵契约"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Mercenary's Contract"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A contract lined with gunpowder and gold. Whoever signed this must be a "
"seasoned operator. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Three "
"Missions: Every expedition now offers 3 randomly assigned bonus missions."
msgstr "一份镶着火药与金边的契约。签署者必是经验丰富的作战者。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁三重任务：每次远征现在提供3个随机分配的额外任务。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Artisan's Contract"
msgid_plural "Artisan's Contracts"
msgstr[0] "工匠契约"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Artisan's Contract"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A finely-crafted contract, demonstrating that the holder can create as well "
"as destroy. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Four Missions: "
"Every expedition now offers 4 randomly assigned bonus missions."
msgstr "一份精工细作的契约，证明持有者既能创造也能毁灭。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁四重任务：每次远征现在提供4个随机分配的额外任务。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Post-human's Contract"
msgid_plural "Post-human's Contracts"
msgstr[0] "后人类契约"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Post-human's Contract"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A contract built from futuristic materials, proving that the holder is "
"beyond human. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Five Missions:"
" Every expedition now offers 5 randomly assigned bonus missions."
msgstr "一份用未来材料打造的契约，证明持有者已超越凡人。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁五重任务：每次远征现在提供5个随机分配的额外任务。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Ordinator's Sigil"
msgid_plural "Ordinator's Sigils"
msgstr[0] "统御者印记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ordinator's Sigil"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange metaphysical artifact will empower the island and unlock a "
"permanent upgrade. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Harder "
"Missions: More challenging bonus missions with greater rewards become "
"available."
msgstr ""
"这件奇异的形而上学神器将增强岛屿的力量并解锁一项永久升级。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁困难任务：更具挑战性的奖励任务将变得可用，并提供更丰厚的回报。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Will of the Island"
msgid_plural "Will of the Islands"
msgstr[0] "岛屿之意志"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Will of the Island'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange metaphysical artifact will empower the island and unlock a "
"permanent upgrade. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Hardest "
"Missions: The most dangerous bonus missions with the greatest rewards become"
" available."
msgstr ""
"这件奇异的形而上学神器将增强岛屿的力量并解锁一项永久升级。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁极难任务：最危险的奖励任务将变得可用，并提供最丰厚的回报。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Vengeance of the Island"
msgid_plural "Vengeance of the Islands"
msgstr[0] "岛屿之复仇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vengeance of the Island'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange metaphysical artifact will empower the island and unlock a "
"permanent upgrade. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Slaughter"
" Missions: A special mission will be assigned during each expedition, "
"rewarding warp shards for killing specific types of enemies."
msgstr ""
"这件奇异的形而上学神器将增强岛屿的力量并解锁一项永久升级。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁屠杀任务：每次远征期间将分配一项特殊任务，通过击杀特定类型的敌人来奖励扭曲碎片。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Inverted Gravity Bubble"
msgid_plural "Inverted Gravity Bubbles"
msgstr[0] "反重力气泡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Inverted Gravity Bubble'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange metaphysical artifact will empower the island and unlock a "
"permanent upgrade. Activate near the Heart of the Island to unlock Landing "
"Flight: While under the warpcloak effect on landing, you gain the power of "
"flight for 60 seconds."
msgstr ""
"这件奇异的形而上学神器将增强岛屿的力量并解锁一项永久升级。在岛屿之心附近激活以解锁着陆飞行：在着陆时处于扭曲斗篷效果下时，你将获得60秒的飞行能力。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "quickheal pill"
msgid_plural "quickheal pills"
msgstr[0] "速愈药丸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'quickheal pill'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This pseudomagical pill will heal all your damaged parts, but only if "
"consumed while on your sanctuary island. No reason to bring this into the "
"field."
msgstr "这颗伪魔法药丸将治愈你所有受损的部位，但仅限于在庇护岛屿上服用时生效。没有理由将其带入野外。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "earthbound pill"
msgid_plural "earthbound pills"
msgstr[0] "地缚药丸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'earthbound pill'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This pseudomagical pill extends the amount of time you can stay earthside by"
" 4 pulses, or about 50% of a normal trip. They're precious, but should help "
"buy time for a difficult extract."
msgstr "这颗伪魔法药丸将延长你在地面停留的时间4个脉冲，大约相当于正常行程的50%。它们很珍贵，但应有助于为困难的撤离争取时间。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "homeward mote"
msgid_plural "homeward motes"
msgstr[0] "归乡微尘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'homeward mote'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"Though visibly little more than a glowing dustbunny, this strange ethereal mote of warp essence reveals, on closer inspection, something more. A tiny, twisting, half-visible thread of shimmering bluish-purple trails away into the sky and far out of sight, unimpeded by any obstacles.\n"
"\n"
"Taking this rare and valuable artifact with you on an expedition is essentially buying life insurance. If you die with this mote in your inventory, you will instead be restored to full health and brought home WITH all items and equipment carried. But this effect will only last for a single expedition. Even if you extract safely, any and all motes carried on your person when you return home will be DESTROYED."
msgstr ""
"尽管看起来不过是一团发光的尘埃，但这缕奇异的以太扭曲精华微尘在仔细观察下揭示了更多。一条微小、扭曲、半隐半现的蓝紫色闪烁细线蜿蜒伸向天空，消失在视线之外，不受任何障碍物阻碍。\n"
"\n"
"携带这件稀有而珍贵的文物进行远征，本质上就是购买人寿保险。如果你在持有此微尘时死亡，你将恢复全部生命值并被带回家，同时保留所有携带的物品和装备。但此效果仅持续单次远征。即使你安全撤离，当你返回家园时，身上携带的任何微尘都将被摧毁。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "skyward beacon"
msgid_plural "skyward beacons"
msgstr[0] "升空信标"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skyward beacon'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This smooth purplish sphere seems like it wants to rise right out of your "
"hand. If you activate it, you will return directly to the island with "
"everything you are carrying."
msgstr "这颗光滑的紫色球体似乎想从你手中直接升起。如果你激活它，你将直接返回岛屿，并携带所有物品。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warp status crystal"
msgid_plural "warp status crystals"
msgstr[0] "扭曲状态水晶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warp status crystal'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A small crystalline orb that pulses with a faint inner light. When "
"activated, it displays detailed information about your current warp status, "
"including pulse count, time remaining, and the effects that will occur at "
"each stage of warp sickness."
msgstr "一颗小型水晶球，内部闪烁着微弱的光芒。激活时，它会显示你当前扭曲状态的详细信息，包括脉冲计数、剩余时间以及扭曲病每个阶段将发生的效果。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warped animal teleporter"
msgid_plural "warped animal teleporters"
msgstr[0] "扭曲动物传送器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warped animal teleporter'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A hand-sized device with a shimmering portal at its core. Unlike a normal "
"pet carrier, this device doesn't store the animal inside - it warps them "
"directly to your sanctuary island, bypassing any weight limitations. "
"Activate near a friendly creature to send it home. The creature will appear "
"at your island when you return from your expedition."
msgstr ""
"一个手掌大小的装置，核心有一个闪烁的传送门。与普通的宠物携带器不同，此装置不将动物存储在内——它直接将它们扭曲传送到你的庇护岛屿，绕过任何重量限制。在友好生物附近激活以将其送回家。该生物将在你从远征返回时出现在你的岛屿上。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warp home focus"
msgid_plural "warp home foci"
msgstr[0] "扭曲归家焦点"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warp home focus', 'str_pl': 'warp home foci'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A small crystalline focus imbued with the power of warp. When activated during an expedition, it can teleport you directly back to your sanctuary island. This item is NOT consumed on use.\n"
"\n"
"Behavior depends on your difficulty settings:\n"
"- Free mode: Works instantly\n"
"- Shard mode: Costs 1 warp shard, cannot use near enemies\n"
"- Other modes: Does not function (use Skyward Beacon or find extraction)"
msgstr ""
"一枚蕴含传送力量的小型水晶焦点。在远征期间激活时，可直接将你传送回庇护岛屿。此物品使用后不会被消耗。\n"
"\n"
"具体效果取决于你的难度设置：\n"
"- 自由模式：立即生效\n"
"- 碎片模式：消耗1个传送碎片，无法在敌人附近使用\n"
"- 其他模式：无法使用（请使用天界信标或寻找撤离点）"

#: .\items.json
msgid "healing salve"
msgid_plural "healing salves"
msgstr[0] "治疗药膏"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'healing salve'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A lump of purplish goo, smooth but yielding, sculptable like clay. If you "
"rub it on a wound, it will immediately heal some of the damage you have "
"taken, but the air of the lower world destabilizes its structure and it will"
" only last a single trip to the surface."
msgstr ""
"一团紫色的粘稠物，触感光滑柔软，可像黏土般塑形。若将其涂抹在伤口上，能立即治愈部分伤害，但下界空气会破坏其结构稳定性，仅能维持单次地表之旅。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warp raft token"
msgid_plural "warp raft tokens"
msgstr[0] "传送筏令牌"

#. ~ Use action unfold_msg for {'str': 'warp raft token'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"The token dissolves into swirling energy that coalesces into a shimmering "
"raft!"
msgstr "令牌溶解为旋转的能量，汇聚成闪烁发光的木筏！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warp raft token'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A small token that pulses with aquatic energy. When activated, it unfolds "
"into a small, slow raft."
msgstr "一枚跃动着水之能量的小型令牌。激活时会展开为缓慢移动的小型木筏。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "wood-floor tokens"
msgid_plural "wood-floor tokens"
msgstr[0] "木地板令牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'wood-floor tokens'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A group of small squares of wood, smooth and polished. You can use them to "
"transform a section of flooring into interlocking wooden planks."
msgstr "一组光滑抛光的小木块。可用它们将部分地板转化为咬合式木板地面。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "flagstone tokens"
msgid_plural "flagstone tokens"
msgstr[0] "石板令牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'flagstone tokens'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A group of small stone stones, rough to the touch. You can use them to "
"transform a section of flooring into mortared flagstones."
msgstr "一组触感粗糙的小石块。可用它们将部分地板转化为砂浆铺设的石板地面。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "sand tokens"
msgid_plural "sand tokens"
msgstr[0] "沙地令牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'sand tokens'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A group of small yellow stones, gritty to the touch yet seemingly nothing "
"ever rubs off. You can use them to transform a section of flooring into fine"
" sand."
msgstr "一组触感粗粝的黄色小石块，表面似乎永不磨损。可用它们将部分地板转化为细沙地面。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Personal Sunblock"
msgid_plural "Personal Sunblocks"
msgstr[0] "个人防晒屏障"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Personal Sunblock'}
#: .\items.json
msgid "The island is protecting you against the sun as long as you are on it."
msgstr "只要你身处岛上，岛屿就会为你抵御阳光伤害。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Personal Windblock"
msgid_plural "Personal Windblocks"
msgstr[0] "个人防风屏障"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Personal Windblock'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"The island is protecting you against the winds as long as you are on it."
msgstr "只要你身处岛上，岛屿就会为你抵御强风影响。"

