#: .\iuse.lua
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You need to be standing next to a working %s to imprint this copyplate."
msgstr "你需要站在正常工作的%s旁边才能刻印此复制板。"

#: .\iuse.lua
#, c-format
msgid "The copyplate hums and glows as it absorbs the %s's schematics!"
msgstr "复制板嗡嗡作响并发光，吸收了%s的图纸！"

#: .\iuse.lua
#, c-format
msgid "You now have an activated %s copyplate."
msgstr "你现在拥有一个已激活的%s复制板。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "The quickheal pill only works on your sanctuary island."
msgstr "快速治疗药丸仅在你的庇护岛屿上有效。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "A warm sensation washes over you as your wounds heal."
msgstr "一股暖流涌遍全身，你的伤口正在愈合。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"You're not on an expedition. Save this for when you need more time "
"earthside."
msgstr "你并非身处远征中。将此留待你需要更多地面时间时使用。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"The pill dissolves on your tongue. You feel the warp's grip on you loosen. "
"(+4 pulses of time)"
msgstr "药丸在你舌间溶解。你感到扭曲对你的掌控松动了。（+4个时间脉冲）"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "The focus pulses weakly but cannot establish a connection."
msgstr "聚焦器微弱脉动但无法建立连接。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Your difficulty settings require a Skyward Beacon or extraction point."
msgstr "你的难度设置需要天界信标或撤离点。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "You're already home. The focus has no effect here."
msgstr "你已在家园。聚焦器在此处无效。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"Hostile creatures nearby disrupt the focus's energy. You cannot use it here!"
msgstr "附近的敌对生物扰乱了聚焦器的能量。你无法在此处使用它！"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "The focus requires a warp shard to activate!"
msgstr "聚焦器需要扭曲碎片来激活！"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"The focus flares with brilliant light. You feel yourself being pulled "
"skyward..."
msgstr "聚焦器迸发出耀眼光芒。你感到自己正被拉向天际……"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"The beacon flickers weakly but nothing happens. Emergency returns are "
"disabled."
msgstr "信标微弱闪烁但无事发生。紧急返回功能已禁用。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "You must find an extraction point (return obelisk) to escape."
msgstr "你必须找到撤离点（返回方尖碑）才能逃脱。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "You're already home. The beacon has no effect here."
msgstr "你已在家园。信标在此处无效。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid ""
"The beacon flares with brilliant light. You feel yourself being pulled "
"skyward..."
msgstr "信标迸发出耀眼光芒。你感到自己正被拉向天际……"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Warp Status Crystal"
msgstr "扭曲状态水晶"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Grace Period: %d pulses\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"宽限期：%d个脉冲\n"
"\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Current Pulse: %d\n"
msgstr "当前脉冲：%d\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Pulse Interval: %d minutes\n"
msgstr "脉冲间隔：%d分钟\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Difficulty: %s\n"
msgstr "难度：%s\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Current Expedition: %s\n"
msgstr "当前远征：%s\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Pulses until disintegration: %d"
msgstr "距离崩解剩余脉冲：%d"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "STATUS: %s (Intensity %d/%d)\n"
msgstr "状态：%s（强度 %d/%d）\n"

#: .\main.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Time until sickness begins: ~%d minutes"
msgstr "距离疾病发作时间：约%d分钟"

#: .\main.lua .\warp_sickness.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Safe pulses remaining: %d\n"
msgstr "剩余安全脉冲次数：%d\n"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "STATUS: STABLE\n"
msgstr "状态：稳定\n"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Stage 1: Warp Stability"
msgstr "阶段一：跃迁稳定"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Grace period. No effects. You feel fine."
msgstr "宽限期。无不良影响。你感觉良好。"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Stage 2: Warp Sickness"
msgstr "阶段二：跃迁不适"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "Intensity 1. -2 to all stats. Mild discomfort."
