#: .\mapgen_sky_island.json
msgid "sky island"
msgstr "天空岛屿"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Reach the exit portal!"
msgstr "突袭：抵达出口传送门！"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Reach the exit portal!'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"If you want to get home with your stuff, you'll need to reach the nearby "
"exit portal. It's the only thing that can bring you back to your sanctuary "
"island in one piece."
msgstr "若想带着物品回家，你需要抵达附近的出口传送门。这是唯一能让你完好返回庇护岛屿的途径。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 10 Zombies"
msgstr "突袭：击杀 10 只僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 10 Zombies'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"Zombies have absorbed latent energies which must be released. Kill at least "
"10 zombified creatures before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "僵尸吸收了必须释放的潜在能量。在返回庇护所前至少击杀 10 只僵尸化生物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 50 Zombies"
msgstr "突袭：击杀 50 只僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 50 Zombies'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"Zombies have absorbed latent energies which must be released. Kill at least "
"50 zombified creatures before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "僵尸吸收了必须释放的潜在能量。在返回庇护所前至少击杀 50 只僵尸化生物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 100 Zombies"
msgstr "突袭：击杀 100 只僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 100 Zombies'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"Zombies have absorbed latent energies which must be released. Kill at least "
"100 zombified creatures before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "僵尸吸收了必须释放的潜在能量。在返回庇护所前至少击杀 100 只僵尸化生物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill a Mi-Go"
msgstr "突袭：击杀一只米-戈"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill a Mi-Go'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"The mi-go have absorbed latent energies which must be released. Kill at "
"least one mi-go creature before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "米-戈吸收了必须释放的潜在能量。在返回庇护所前至少击杀一只米-戈生物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 3 Nether Creatures"
msgstr "突袭：击杀 3 只下界生物"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 3 Nether Creatures'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A rift to another dimension has drained latent energies which must be "
"released. Kill at least 3 nether-born creatures before returning to your "
"sanctuary."
msgstr "通往其他维度的裂隙耗尽了必须释放的潜在能量。在返回庇护所前至少击杀 3 只下界原生生物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 5 Birds"
msgstr "突袭任务：击杀5只鸟类"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 5 Birds'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"Even the local wildlife has started absorbing latent warp energy. Kill at "
"least 5 non-zombie birds before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "连当地的野生动物也开始吸收潜在的扭曲能量。在返回你的避难所之前，至少击杀5只非僵尸鸟类。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill 5 Mammals"
msgstr "突袭任务：击杀5只哺乳动物"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill 5 Mammals'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"Even the local wildlife has started absorbing latent warp energy. Kill at "
"least 5 non-zombie mammals before returning to your sanctuary."
msgstr "连当地的野生动物也开始吸收潜在的扭曲能量。在返回你的避难所之前，至少击杀5只非僵尸哺乳动物。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Find the warp shards!"
msgstr "突袭任务：寻找扭曲碎片！"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Find the warp shards!'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A very small cluster of warp energy has left shards behind at this location."
" All you need to do is find and retrieve them. There may be threats nearby, "
"but unlike most tasks, no special guards are on-site. A minimal reward, but "
"little risk."
msgstr "一小簇扭曲能量在此地留下了碎片。你只需要找到并回收它们。附近可能有威胁，但与大多数任务不同，现场没有特殊守卫。奖励微薄，但风险也小。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Clear zombie cluster"
msgstr "突袭任务：清理僵尸群"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Clear zombie cluster'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A handful of zombies are congregating at a location where warp resonance is "
"high. Clear them out for a minimal reward of warp shards."
msgstr "一小群僵尸聚集在扭曲共振强烈的地点。清理它们以获得微薄的扭曲碎片奖励。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Clear zombie horde"
msgstr "突袭任务：清理僵尸潮"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Clear zombie horde'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A horde of low level zombies are congregating at a location where warp "
"resonance is high. Clear them out for a small reward of warp shards."
msgstr "一大群低阶僵尸聚集在扭曲共振强烈的地点。清理它们以获得少量扭曲碎片奖励。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Clear evolved zombies"
msgstr "突袭任务：清理进化僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Clear evolved zombies'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A swarm of evolved zombies are congregating at a location where warp "
"resonance is high. Clear them out for a medium reward of warp shards."
msgstr "一群进化僵尸聚集在扭曲共振强烈的地点。清理它们以获得中等数量的扭曲碎片奖励。"

#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Clear evolved horde"
msgstr "突袭任务：清理进化僵尸潮"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Clear evolved horde'}'
#: .\missions.json
