#: .\missions.json
msgid "RAID: Kill zombie lord"
msgstr "突袭任务：击杀僵尸领主"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'RAID: Kill zombie lord'}'
#: .\missions.json
msgid ""
"A single supremely powerful zombie has been found at a location where warp "
