msgid "Sky Island"
msgstr "天空岛"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d items from the red room were teleported home with you!"
msgstr "%d件来自红房间的物品随你传送回家了！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Quick Expedition"
msgstr "快速远征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Normal time limit (2 hours grace). Exits will be close together."
msgstr "正常时间限制（2小时宽限期）。出口将紧密相邻。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Large Expedition"
msgstr "大型远征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Double time limit (4 hours grace). Exits scattered over wider area."
msgstr "双倍时间限制（4小时宽限期）。出口分散在更广区域。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Extended Expedition"
msgstr "延长远征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Triple time limit (6 hours grace). Exits very far away."
msgstr "三倍时间限制（6小时宽限期）。出口相距甚远。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Field"
msgstr "田野"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"Arrive in a barren field. Usually wilderness, but could be an empty lot in "
"town."
msgstr "抵达一片荒芜田野。通常是荒野，但也可能是城镇中的空地。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Basement"
msgstr "地下室"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Arrive inside an underground basement. Usually suburbia."
msgstr "抵达地下室内。通常是郊区。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Rooftop"
msgstr "屋顶"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Arrive on a building roof. Usually houses, one story up."
msgstr "抵达建筑屋顶。通常是房屋，向上一个楼层。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Science Lab"
msgstr "科学实验室"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"Arrive in a subterranean science lab. DANGEROUS! Costs 1 Labs Catalyst. You "
"will be sealed inside - bring an exit strategy!"
msgstr "抵达一处地下科学实验室。危险！消耗1个实验室催化剂。你将被封闭在内——请准备好撤离方案！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You feel reality shift around you..."
msgstr "你感到周围的现实发生了扭曲……"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Warp energy lifts you into the air!"
msgstr "跃迁能量将你托举至空中！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Your feet touch the ground as the warp flight fades."
msgstr "随着跃迁飞行的消退，你的双脚触及地面。"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d island animal%s returned home safely!"
msgstr "%d只岛屿动物%s安全返回家园！"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d warped animal%s arrived at your island!"
msgstr "%d只跃迁动物%s抵达了你的岛屿！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You are already on an expedition!"
msgstr "你已在探险中！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "ERROR: Could not determine position!"
